</script></div><div data-rid="972a9b8e-5e78-41da-91ed-f5e353ef2aa5" class="r-1fgwbbm"><div data-rid="cbd4aee0-f1da-4b0d-93ba-46d984a02049" class="r-u1mivv"><div data-rid="a3df492b-9245-4ab5-a74f-48d6a5b3f319" class="r-2hddx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.60)">Wellness Research · </span><span style="color: #0D9488">Expert Interview</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="36d578f3-d063-42f5-8264-1f73b87fa482" class="r-fk2lyy"><div data-rid="79aa7d37-cebd-4aa0-80b0-9bf316a85659" class="r-b4kn1t"><div data-rid="887ee54e-f210-4c2b-86dc-e405a69b88b8" class="r-1e86yi6"><div data-rid="f3336e97-44ff-4d39-8053-d206767e3cef" class="r-1lardlo"><div data-rid="4392e693-fcf7-45e2-ace5-2d467fbe7c3d" class="r-lfjp7e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">⚕️ Health & Wellness Interview</span></div></div><div data-rid="a306326b-15b3-4b41-a66a-594547fb27f0" class="r-u1arot"><div data-rid="22ff5a05-db41-462a-b9a3-70f09be910e0" class="r-1tlhl7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">A Pharmacist Reveals<br>The Secret Problem<br>With Over 1,000,000<br>People's Lungs, And He<br>Created The&nbsp;Solution</span></div></div><div data-rid="b23d72b3-0152-46f8-abec-b97226ebec50" class="r-1iexcp8"><div data-rid="ae5cdcd8-dc84-41a3-a75c-1fa5c24cdb3f" class="r-1tbv3mk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Tired of struggling to breathe? Tired of<br>waking up congested, coughing through the<br>day, and running out of energy by noon?<br>Millions of people are stuck in this cycle. We<br>sat down with the pharmacist whose<br>formula has now helped over 1,000,000 of<br>them.</span></div></div><div data-rid="f78cc1e4-edb7-47c0-896c-8bce8e7c12a2" class="r-ba8lek"><div data-rid="88229b6c-1ef9-49a5-98db-ff123b87a1c5" class="r-1xb9ew3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">By Sarah Mitchell, Health Editor · February 2026</span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a228601d-92e3-4f75-ba36-6c65caaf2f9f" class="r-zmp4a6"><div data-rid="d880881a-01ba-4717-ac31-912b1bb81290" class="r-4skyjn"><div data-rid="81133ee6-2c77-4222-a6b5-f5701349a818" class="r-nrm4sw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">We hear the same story again and again.</span></div></div><div data-rid="c01cc96e-23c0-4e5c-8fcb-11c0a8e5f035" class="r-j8pwz8"><div data-rid="1c8b6dde-0303-472a-9488-0c353b4210a2" class="r-u9e13y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Someone starts noticing they're more<br>winded than they used to be. A nagging<br>cough that won't clear up. Congestion<br>every morning. Energy that disappears by<br>lunch. They've tried everything they can<br>think of - and nothing seems to get to the<br>root of it.</span></div></div><div data-rid="e4d2d310-8a42-4dec-b4fa-af7a5f72cf10" class="r-169odpu"><div data-rid="b2b2b82c-007c-4544-b32c-a74f2a257b94" class="r-1tc0agi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">They feel stuck. Frustrated. Like their lungs<br>are working against them.</span></div></div><div data-rid="203060ab-4cda-438f-aca9-90563c9caaa7" class="r-1uavjjc"><div data-rid="b1264f37-f545-440c-875a-fea103530874" class="r-1w1d75g alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">We wanted to understand why so many<br>people feel this way - and what can actually<br>be done about it. So we sat down with the<br>man whose respiratory wellness formula<br>has now been tried by over 1,000,000<br>people.</span></div></div><div data-rid="86a34b11-1b26-4a89-b080-0e53c00f7503" class="r-17asjxi"><div data-rid="08f83722-1ae5-478a-8343-06475113fa26" class="r-8w6l8d"><div data-rid="524612ac-c9df-463c-895b-0342e2ab97fc" class="r-ttxj7c alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Dr. Chris Jackson, Pharm.D.</span></div></div><div data-rid="ce360f79-3656-4b40-b4c9-ef025d6221c7" class="r-1ox7mwz"><div data-rid="28ca0c98-7d56-4f46-a8af-d94de3be6884" class="r-1sqe1cn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Doctor of Pharmacy & Founder of<br>BetterBrand. Formulator of BetterLungs®<br>Mullein + Chlorophyll. Former U.S. Army<br>Combat Medic.</span></div></div></div><picture data-rid="bc15bcae-8306-4e31-89fe-50573b47653e" class="r-1uax5sk"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/30335833-4e1d-414f-9b08-5b4d90f706ab?width=706" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/30335833-4e1d-414f-9b08-5b4d90f706ab?width=706" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/30335833-4e1d-414f-9b08-5b4d90f706ab?width=706" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/30335833-4e1d-414f-9b08-5b4d90f706ab" class="r-avacpy" loading="eager" alt="Middle-aged man in a blue shirt speaking into a microphone during a podcast-style interview in a home office with bookshelves."/></picture><div data-rid="a764c14e-21fa-422e-b2ca-696fbc27777c" class="r-14wnt5f"></div><div data-rid="285e2311-6a2c-4065-887d-2eeaefc9d7ff" class="r-1n98brh"><div data-rid="42bc2356-f63a-4671-8e68-c910b2c74eb6" class="r-nuottn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Part 1</span></div></div><div data-rid="e1086380-adad-41c5-b045-0677d9d1046e" class="r-1t0n4pl"><div data-rid="84173da4-e855-4abd-a0fe-8d1dbefff1f2" class="r-14o2g57 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">"Here's What's Actually<br>Happening Inside Your Lungs -<br>And Why You Feel Stuck"</span></div></div><div data-rid="df4c1cc1-1d67-4b67-9951-5f3fcfd09093" class="r-jy0hn2"><div data-rid="c43cc78a-5eef-4d8c-9ed8-456c30dd9748" class="r-ufq31l"><div data-rid="9156ecf7-32d8-42ef-8953-c6665cab9590" class="r-11a6vva"><div data-rid="9194e406-d55e-4f19-a43f-0521750e2e04" class="r-1cvq0zj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sarah Mitchell - Health Editor</span></div></div><div data-rid="f5c0b05e-7f1a-421d-bd40-cfde4f7a0480" class="r-15lurg6"><div data-rid="a2a3fcb9-b00c-4fe7-ad24-be268ee77d78" class="r-eor0xz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">So many people tell us they're coughing<br>constantly, always congested, and exhausted<br>- but they can't figure out why. What's<br>actually going on?</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="ad825f25-2bb5-4147-9dde-c4fe61336722" class="r-z959da"><div data-rid="f0ccbe1c-f903-4cc3-b4c5-0cca68c5774d" class="r-1wtbjuy"><div data-rid="7821aec5-22cc-4472-967e-1edf3785995a" class="r-16iaia8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Dr. Chris Jackson, Pharm.D.</span></div></div><div data-rid="62911095-0c46-4c7d-ad5f-0c6b06ab94c4" class="r-1xkq2w8"><div data-rid="d30f9a09-beb4-4580-9cab-51c13a4836e7" class="r-wny2c8"><div data-rid="4d3b3c30-2a01-46df-8d92-54e82dbadf58" class="r-anfe5z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">What most people don't realize is that<br>respiratory congestion accumulates<br>gradually over a lifetime. Every breath<br>brings in environmental particles -<br>dust, allergens, pollutants, even<br>chemicals from everyday cleaning<br>products. Your lungs have a natural<br>clearance system - tiny hairs called<br>cilia that sweep mucus upward - but<br>it's slow. And over decades, buildup<br>can exceed what your body clears on<br>its own.</span></div></div><div data-rid="8637c8f3-4b73-4243-ac8b-0bf54a40baf9" class="r-13rnq3z"><div data-rid="bc2980c3-70ff-4c29-8a8f-ecd03a32ba90" class="r-oqz6hn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">You just feel a little more tired. A little<br>more congested. A little more<br>winded each year. And you think it's<br>normal.</span></div></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="34ddef26-ae0c-4554-96f4-8a3fe3b90065" class="r-1rkfud6"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ae47b026-887b-4fdd-9a8c-3198293e118b?width=706" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ae47b026-887b-4fdd-9a8c-3198293e118b?width=706" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ae47b026-887b-4fdd-9a8c-3198293e118b?width=706" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ae47b026-887b-4fdd-9a8c-3198293e118b" class="r-1fq9jxt" loading="lazy" alt="Lung Strength Over Time — declining curves with dashed 'Natural aging' and solid 'With environmental buildup'; shaded Age 40–50: 'Where most people start noticing symptoms'."/></picture><div data-rid="e6ef1f04-b302-40f9-a6fa-2366fd08a8cb" class="r-9uqfu5"><div data-rid="2108a892-d357-4334-a458-f79f048fd4c4" class="r-mepdas"><div data-rid="eb66b7bc-b0df-47de-91fb-153e6e62f6b8" class="r-19wklhl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">💡 Key Insight</span></div></div><div data-rid="a5a53f1c-a31c-45a4-8a00-cb67ea7c2f5c" class="r-r183dw"><div data-rid="e4b4871d-3882-42f6-a732-17fde2f0d50f" class="r-1jk2ezj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Your lungs can gradually accumulate<br>congestion from years of normal<br>environmental exposure. This buildup<br>happens so slowly most people<br>attribute the effects - low energy,<br>shallow breathing, persistent coughing<br>- to simply "getting older."</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="6a968ade-bc07-43f4-a63e-94d4f4b7339e" class="r-z4kfso"><div data-rid="b08e3284-6211-4842-94dd-a7b83cd04351" class="r-1yndma7"><div data-rid="7e2d9a47-69c3-442c-b4c5-4ead74dd814a" class="r-1k7e2df"><div data-rid="048950c9-69f5-4f76-9e56-4b6f6835fc73" class="r-1jpimj6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sarah Mitchell</span></div></div><div data-rid="3fbe0392-4f0f-4877-9d53-03b7de5fdc36" class="r-1f1dnke"><div data-rid="ad3492cc-4211-430e-818a-d2939c9fa122" class="r-hqsqo5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">So it's not necessarily that something is<br>wrong - it's that there's a buildup most<br>people don't know about?</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="70fbec0c-30ce-4631-87a0-280c4e973a8e" class="r-211wtj"><div data-rid="82b505aa-28eb-4bae-882f-a3a6c9d1ecde" class="r-7cdh2q"><div data-rid="49d75fbb-d806-4fa2-8ed1-bbe181604d20" class="r-o031hx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Dr. Jackson</span></div></div><div data-rid="7c1f71f1-856d-43cb-9792-7d49feeb13c2" class="r-5lj9uo"><div data-rid="16eadf0b-3144-4768-95cf-32753599136d" class="r-1ade6hp"><div data-rid="3db4849d-73a2-412b-829f-817eb1813c23" class="r-1m8rbe5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Exactly. Think of it like this: if you<br>never deep-cleaned your home's air<br>ducts, after 20 or 30 years, the airflow<br>wouldn't be what it was when the<br>system was new. Your lungs are the<br>same way. They may be perfectly<br>healthy - but decades of accumulated<br>residue can reduce how efficiently<br>they work.</span></div></div><div data-rid="c42fce83-1294-4e49-834b-a2b2b1d04e19" class="r-1e0bxvl"><div data-rid="47e4321e-fb88-4dbf-b81c-a551c6c38108" class="r-2aczqb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">This is where I saw an opportunity.<br>Not to replace anything people are<br>already doing for their health, but to<br>add a layer of support that addresses<br>this specific buildup that nothing else<br>was really targeting.</span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="227bf3eb-f828-47c4-9409-586c0db7c36a" class="r-p6yxex"></div><div data-rid="05af4648-5b61-41d1-b68b-9fe2a473fea5" class="r-gndldk"><div data-rid="7043a09b-f9df-4452-a518-662c46be6571" class="r-174jaw1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Part 2</span></div></div><div data-rid="66305ce1-6269-4ca0-9d8c-160da31d025d" class="r-wbwo73"><div data-rid="c9fd3c79-90a6-4db1-9d45-646d8e61b125" class="r-9hber4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">"Why I Created BetterLungs® -<br>And the Personal Story Behind<br>It"</span></div></div><div data-rid="f52ad9de-5dad-444d-9130-7471459b9d4c" class="r-1eo2jgt"><div data-rid="cba6c074-988a-406a-ae4a-e1c9af0f042d" class="r-13tzkag"><div data-rid="7fa76729-d5bd-45df-a75f-d8e312d25542" class="r-16eyvia"><div data-rid="85e9d660-4476-4f71-8e05-0941b122108a" class="r-uaai8l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sarah Mitchell</span></div></div><div data-rid="f6f5e013-2aa0-4206-9133-c2c4d6d840b2" class="r-5bgvz7"><div data-rid="ea279363-ae12-4c6e-a5ca-335d85f02542" class="r-1w9kwcf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">This clearly isn't just professional for you.<br>What drove you to create this?</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="4892fd9f-7afe-43df-ac31-a5ea962bb9ea" class="r-f91tbi"><div data-rid="a505c247-8935-41da-98bf-9f9e7307d59b" class="r-3vtna8"><div data-rid="ac7f1c93-bf26-4148-be16-a0d8a446a16a" class="r-1bxycpx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Dr. Jackson</span></div></div><div data-rid="b7167460-a488-4e6e-9738-65768849b90e" class="r-1xprr4u"><div data-rid="da87f021-bfd4-4f4d-8936-e46752c30bc9" class="r-z6r3oa"><div data-rid="38f9a96b-daa4-44c3-a25b-e50f36f2d840" class="r-v7vl80 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">I lost multiple family members who<br>struggled with respiratory health.</span></div></div><div data-rid="ccf7effb-8aaf-4193-b715-ae03269eac9f" class="r-1tbypbs"><div data-rid="ed076d1f-8806-4f7e-b38f-ad80b99c8e0c" class="r-m6ghwf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Watching someone you love struggle<br>to breathe - and feeling like you<br>should be able to do more - changes<br>you.</span></div></div><div data-rid="3a7b4e56-480f-4d51-a360-4905e4898fa3" class="r-1pjqtn6"><div data-rid="870930f2-9dac-476d-9f67-db578a15172f" class="r-1bjdzfb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">In the Army, as a combat medic, I saw<br>respiratory issues from a different<br>angle. Soldiers exposed to harsh<br>environments. And when they came<br>home, they didn't always have great<br>options for ongoing respiratory<br>support.</span></div></div><div data-rid="397385e1-e0ec-4148-b702-7a6b4ab827c1" class="r-ww7x52"><div data-rid="c0e1e895-7403-4453-a18a-2ea31366c792" class="r-w9af93 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">So when I became a pharmacist, I<br>made it my focus. I studied every<br>herbal respiratory tradition -<br>European, Chinese, Appalachian folk<br>medicine. The same plant kept<br>showing up everywhere: mullein.</span></div></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="85151e83-fea4-46c4-908c-0f7189006ab2" class="r-3lkmnr"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/6ef45cf7-dee5-4cf1-8090-367f134053e2?width=706" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/6ef45cf7-dee5-4cf1-8090-367f134053e2?width=706" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/6ef45cf7-dee5-4cf1-8090-367f134053e2?width=706" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/6ef45cf7-dee5-4cf1-8090-367f134053e2" class="r-rihqc" loading="eager" alt="Lab technician in white coat examining a long dried plant sprig on a stainless table with jars, beakers, and notes."/></picture><picture data-rid="c9d03058-a20b-45f1-bd22-48d994e962b3" class="r-1mjjz9i"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/390367d6-0c20-4008-b5bf-e5bc82e3f261?width=706" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/390367d6-0c20-4008-b5bf-e5bc82e3f261?width=706" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/390367d6-0c20-4008-b5bf-e5bc82e3f261?width=706" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/390367d6-0c20-4008-b5bf-e5bc82e3f261" class="r-p56400" loading="eager" alt="Mullein (Verbascum) with tall yellow flower spike and fuzzy green leaves in a sunlit meadow."/></picture><div data-rid="d4fede26-6bf0-47c7-a158-c7259f2bce72" class="r-1t0obcv"><div data-rid="99f2ed03-1a1f-4ebb-87a2-c38b119e1c72" class="r-889th9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Mullein (Verbascum thapsus) - used for respiratory support for<br>over 2,000 years.</span></div></div><div data-rid="f82607bc-ba65-4cb1-b1e9-5083607b4983" class="r-1s4o2q7"><div data-rid="29d28a1a-096c-4f15-89c7-65f3ab7971ae" class="r-15hnd3n"><div data-rid="7f8a85cd-5fc0-4092-bb35-a87385a6da2e" class="r-1uuj3f3"><div data-rid="d84d7f61-5f35-43da-80aa-2c0b3e742686" class="r-1rklj4y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sarah Mitchell</span></div></div><div data-rid="e3c80925-e1bf-4e75-bc2b-37cf50e1a10a" class="r-14xm2zo"><div data-rid="fe739c03-8233-49ec-a23f-258cb6a55296" class="r-ctzo9s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Mullein has been around for centuries. What<br>makes your formulation different from<br>drinking mullein tea?</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="62d4a0ee-c119-4391-9dbd-9ab2a4c242cc" class="r-1v668p7"><div data-rid="871c0344-0b8b-446c-9eaa-824bb8d93c25" class="r-1ngd2so"><div data-rid="edddb1d1-15e4-45d4-a3a2-1ad957e8ff60" class="r-14j814l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Dr. Jackson</span></div></div><div data-rid="6fc91352-5734-4fa2-a5d8-4a45b18b0e08" class="r-1b28w3r"><div data-rid="f637cdcb-b11d-4ad5-93a9-9c089ac179f4" class="r-1qork8i"><div data-rid="3fd2ee21-4d8b-4337-8116-fea42b5cf798" class="r-6smsbe alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Two things. Concentration and<br>combination.</span></div></div><div data-rid="ac589a99-05b7-4778-b3d6-491167d9ef13" class="r-1kk1y4d"><div data-rid="04086d96-8e2e-43f7-836c-399288e2be6b" class="r-59iuh9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">BetterLungs® Mullein + Chlorophyll<br>uses a 10:1 concentrated mullein<br>extract - every dropper contains the<br>active compounds from 10x more<br>mullein leaf than a cup of tea. The<br>saponins - the compounds that help<br>thin and loosen old, stagnant mucus -<br>are present at meaningful levels, not<br>trace am