support your body's<br>ability to clear the old buildup - the<br>stuff that's been sitting in your<br>airways for years. That's a different<br>goal, which is why it feels different for<br>so many people.</span></div></div><div data-rid="20cc32db-9797-4712-abdb-1c6b129d8b1a" class="r-15vlcbh"><div data-rid="0455d9e0-5efc-401f-b8f1-d303c9e306f1" class="r-1bp7xoa alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">And the 365-day guarantee exists<br>because I know this audience. They've<br>been let down before.</span></div></div><div data-rid="92b07f7b-24e0-44b4-90d1-fb9f518c1921" class="r-17phyow"><div data-rid="3b1753ba-8798-4101-98bc-3ef7156ca276" class="r-1yqscp3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">So I'm not asking anyone to trust a<br>promise. I'm asking them to try it and<br>judge for themselves - with a full year<br>to decide.</span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c0c6b5e0-8f45-458b-ab8d-448100997d13" class="r-30gpng"></div><div data-rid="480a06d8-6671-4a83-91bd-5f79d04f151e" class="r-z20u02"><div data-rid="26ad5363-a71d-4c2c-ba1e-3108cd925701" class="r-e2utpx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Part 5</span></div></div><div data-rid="b12ab702-b011-43c9-9e76-2e7f669e1a44" class="r-duxnfs"><div data-rid="9f5833a4-421a-4d1d-a3c4-95daf912d3d7" class="r-yz8d06 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">"What Should Someone Expect<br>If They Start Today?"</span></div></div><div data-rid="e3bef32f-acf4-4475-abef-958e1f0e1a8d" class="r-o8w8a4"><div data-rid="e9a58f7e-8d70-4d5c-8beb-da6ad8a51d97" class="r-10io4y4"><div data-rid="19a9a9ee-a1df-4828-9055-146f7d8d2133" class="r-82jle5"><div data-rid="5e020d44-af6d-46a7-a2be-2c82fbc44c70" class="r-jzrkv1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sarah Mitchell</span></div></div><div data-rid="30e4f7b4-7740-4ddb-bd41-c99fc5c4b1ea" class="r-1sudzj6"><div data-rid="82c20054-9f36-4527-8eb4-89544fe06b18" class="r-ai6suw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Walk us through the realistic timeline.</span></div></div></div><div data-rid